"use strict";(self.webpackChunksoulmatters_ro=self.webpackChunksoulmatters_ro||[]).push([[1645],{1645:i=>{i.exports=JSON.parse('{"author":"Andra Cozma","date":"2019-09-09T18:12:50.000Z","slug":"sfatosilor-dati-mi-pace","status":"publish","title":"Sf\u0103to\u0219ilor, da\u021bi-mi pace!","excerpt":"\xcen cele mai frumoase momente ale vie\u021bii tale, apar acele persoane care vor vrea s\u0103 te sf\u0103tuiasc\u0103. Sfaturi nesolicitate, evident.  ","article":"\xcen cele mai frumoase momente ale vie\u021bii tale, apar acele persoane care vor vrea s\u0103 te sf\u0103tuiasc\u0103. Sfaturi nesolicitate, evident. Totul va \xeencepe cu \u201etrebuie s\u0103\u2026\u201d \u201eaveti grij\u0103 cu\u2026\u201d etc.\\r\\n\\r\\nMomentul acela \xeen care po\u021bi g\u0103si cele mai multe persoane sf\u0103toase/**m\xb2** este atunci c\xe2nd alegi sa devii p\u0103rinte.\\r\\n\\r\\nTotul incepe cu:  \\r\\n\u2013 Sc\u0103pa\u021bi de c\xe2ini!  \\r\\n\u2013 O s\u0103 v\u0103 lega\u021bi, de acum nu mai face\u021bi ce vre\u021bi voi!  \\r\\n\u2013 Ehe, nop\u021bi nedormite \u0219i multe necazuri!  \\r\\n\u2013 Adio placerilor proprii, o s\u0103 vede\u021bi voi!  \\r\\n\u2013 Nu mai aduce\u021bi oameni \xeen cas\u0103!  \\r\\n\u2013 Scoate\u021bi plantele din camer\u0103!  \\r\\n\u2013 Cump\u0103ra\u021bi doar produse naturale!  \\r\\n\u2013 Nu c\u0103ra nici m\u0103car o sticla de ap\u0103!  \\r\\n\u2013 Vezi s\u0103 nu r\u0103ce\u0219ti!  \\r\\n\u2013 Vezi c\u0103 umbl\u0103 nu \u0219tiu ce microb, f\u0103 vaccin!  \\r\\n\u2013 Nu m\xe2nca prostii c\u0103 te \xeemboln\u0103ve\u0219ti!  \\r\\n\u2013 Nu te enerva c\u0103 \xeei faci r\u0103u copilului(p\u0103i, pot de voi?)  \\r\\n\u2013 Nu te obosi prea tare, ca s\u0103 nu p\u0103\u021be\u0219ti ceva  \\r\\n\u2013 Cred c\u0103 s-a \xeen\u021beles ideea.\\r\\n\\r\\nCu alte cuvinte, nu face nimic din ce crezi tu c\u0103 e bine, c\u0103 tu nu \u0219tii de fapt nimic. Dac\u0103 faci totul cum te taie capul, vei avea parte de priviri ustur\u0103toare, cuvinte dezabropatoare \u0219i mustr\u0103ri repetate.\\r\\n\\r\\nM\u0103i oameni buni dar voi v\u0103 auzi\u021bi pe voi \xeen\u0219iv\u0103 m\u0103car o clip\u0103?\\r\\n\\r\\nV-am \xeentrebat eu de vorb\u0103 cu privire la via\u021ba mea? Am l\u0103sat impresia c\u0103 doresc asisten\u021b\u0103 \xeen momentele importante ale vie\u021bii mele? Considera\u021bi c\u0103 f\u0103r\u0103 indica\u021biile voastre, eu nu \xeemi pot organiza via\u021ba?\\r\\n\\r\\nM\u0103, c\xe2t de handicapat po\u021bi crede un om de ajungi sa ii dai indica\u021bii despre ce s\u0103 fac\u0103 cu via\u021ba lui? \xcen setea voastr\u0103 de a v\u0103 sim\u021bi importan\u021bi sfato\u0219ilor, jigni\u021bi omul!\\r\\n\\r\\nFiecare viitor p\u0103rinte \u0219tie ce are de f\u0103cut \u0219i dac\u0103 nu \u0219tie chiar tot, \xeenva\u021b\u0103. L\u0103sa\u021bi-l s\u0103 fie a\u0219a cum consider\u0103 c\u0103 trebuie s\u0103 fie el. Cu siguran\u021b\u0103 va fi mult mai echilibrat dec\xe2t a\u021bi fost voi \u0219i progeniturile progeniturilor voastre. Cu siguran\u021b\u0103, are deja o via\u021b\u0103 mult mai armonioas\u0103 dec\xe2t a voastr\u0103 \xeen care zilnic v\u0103 zboar\u0103 jigniri \u0219i farfurii prin cas\u0103.\\r\\n\\r\\nVede\u021bi-v\u0103 sf\u0103to\u0219ilor de via\u021ba voastr\u0103 c\u0103 la acest capitol voi mai ave\u021bi de lucrat. Spune\u021bi c\u0103 \xeemi vre\u021bi binele? Aiurea. Vre\u021bi s\u0103 v\u0103 auzi\u021bi vorbind. M\u0103 agasa\u021bi cu indica\u021biile voastre \u0219i ca atare, ve\u021bi fi da\u021bi la o parte. Fiecare om are dreptul s\u0103 fac\u0103 ce consider\u0103 de cuviin\u021b\u0103 cu via\u021ba sa!\\r\\n\\r\\nCei care nu au reu\u0219it s\u0103 \xee\u0219i men\u021bin\u0103 via\u021ba \u0219i familia \xeen armonie, \xee\u0219i vor c\u0103uta o importan\u021b\u0103 \xeen via\u021ba altuia prin sfaturi \u0219i indica\u021bii nesolicitate. De fiecare dat\u0103 \u0219i f\u0103r\u0103 excep\u021bii, din p\u0103cate.\\r\\n    ","previous":{"slug":"instincte-si-copilasi","title":"Instincte \u0219i copila\u0219i"},"next":{"slug":"obisnuinta-abuzului-emotional","title":"Obi\u0219nuin\u021ba abuzului emo\u021bional"}}')}}]);